			<div class="content" id="post-content-4157728">
									

<p>Spooky, right?</p>
<p>I wrote this as a non-SCP thing when I got the idea, then realised how heavily SCP-related it was, then put together this version in an afternoon. It's the shortest thing I've ever written, and I probably spent as much time on the formatting as I did on the text &#8212; it was one of those real &quot;bolt from the blue&quot; type concepts. I lukewarm-posted, with essentially no changes after getting critique, but my heart goes out to the two or three people who looked it over beforehand and gave me the confidence to post.</p>
<p>I'm super glad to see you all like this sort of thing as much as I do :)</p>

